            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">i get mine at cvs/pharmacy and ekard i never pay more than .99 for them. i can get them at the ever most awsome flea market for like .25 i got all of my star wars pez therer and paid less than 3.00 for all of them and i also got another set(not foe sale sorry ) at the drug store for .88 a pez</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
