          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 09-04-98 04:14 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I have found some neat pez at yard sales usually for 5 to 50 cents. I have found a micky mouse pez, a chicken pez, and many others. The trick is to go every Saturday and just look.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
