            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I found a Pony-Go-Round (orange head - value=$115), a Mr. Ugly (value=$50), a fat-eared bunny and a no-foot snowman all on the same trip! I paid $5 for each of these. Woohoo!!</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
