          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>doppel</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 10-29-98 09:12 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I bought a n/f snowman MIB for 10$,two fat eared bunnies for 5$ each,a soft head wonderwoman(mint) for 6$,a truck mvbl wheels(mint) 5$ , a metal hinged red and green regular(mint) for 4$, all from the same antique store but at different times</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>ZNICK</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 11-05-98 11:17 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I found a Mickey "C" for 50 cents at a flea market last week. BUT BEWARE! At the last antique mall I hit there were tons of current PEZ...all selling from $10 to $15.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
